{"word":"H5001 - נָאַם - nâʼam - naw-am' - Say - சொல்லு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>נָאַם"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>nâʼam"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>naw-am'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Say / சொல்லு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - சொல்லு, உரை, விளம்பு, கேள்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to prophesy, to utter a prophecy, to speak as prophet, to sax (Qal) to utter a prophecy, to speak as prophet"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; properly to <i>whisper</i>, that is, (by implication) to <i>utter</i> as an oracle: - say."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H5001 - נָאַם - nâʼam - naw-am'/5001\">H5001</a>, <a href=\"#/H5002 - נְאֻם - nᵉʼum - neh-oom'/5002\">H5002</a>"}]}